export SHELL="${SHELL:-/bin/sh}"
export SHLVL="${SHLVL:-1}"
export PWD="${PWD:-/home/bhbuilder/benchpress}"
export LOGNAME="${LOGNAME:-bhbuilder}"
export HOME="${HOME:-/home/bhbuilder}"
export PATH="${PATH:-/usr/bin:/bin}"
export LD_LIBRARY_PATH="${LD_LIBRARY_PATH:-/home/bhbuilder/.local/lib:}"
export _="${_:-/home/bhbuilder/bohrium-by-night/run_benchmark.py}"
export BH_CONFIG=/tmp/bh-job-acd5d064-c8b0-4aa6-b06b-5e91c749d30b.sh_0.config.ini

#SBATCH -J 'Wire World'
#SBATCH -o /tmp/bh-slurm-%%j.out
#SBATCH -e /tmp/bh-slurm-%%j.err
echo "[bridge]
type = bridge
children = node

[visualizer]
type = ve
children = node
impl = /home/bhbuilder/.local/lib/libbh_ve_visualizer.so

[proxy]
type = vem
port = 4200
impl = /home/bhbuilder/.local/lib/libbh_proxy_server.so
children = node

[cluster]
type = vem
children = node
impl = /home/bhbuilder/.local/lib/libbh_vem_cluster.so

[node]
type = vem
children = cpu
impl = /home/bhbuilder/.local/lib/libbh_vem_node.so
timing = false

[cpu]
type = ve
compiler_cmd = "gcc -I/home/bhbuilder/.local/include -I/home/bhbuilder/.local/include/bohrium -I/home/bhbuilder/.local/share/bohrium/include -lm -O3 -march=native -fopenmp -fPIC -std=c99 -x c -shared - -o "
object_path = /home/bhbuilder/.local/var/bohrium/objects
kernel_path = /home/bhbuilder/.local/var/bohrium/kernels
